{"tid":2169272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反共桌遊-逆統戰 將開發steam&手遊版！","createTime":"2020-08-22T11:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T19:06:03.000Z","uid":370508,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49263d7d8b406fb629203f4770a64e41283777f1","tid":2169272,"uid":370508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:03:58.000Z","msg":"反共史詩桌遊《逆統戰：致地與海的革命者》每一位贊助人，都是下一場革命的金主<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tx07j38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTx07j38.png&h=645a1f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《逆統戰》是 ESC 團隊籌備多年的桌遊新作，其名稱取自 2017 年一篇網路投書提到的「逆統戰力」，遊戲中玩家可別扮演滿洲、台灣、香港、藏國、維吾爾、哈薩克、蒙古與反賊等陣營，來對抗實力強大的紅軍陣營。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>根據募資頁面指出，官方強調募資達 900 萬將啟動電子遊戲開發計畫，將《逆統戰》搬上 Steam 平台，若達到 1,000 萬則決定啟動手遊開發計畫。</strong><br />\n<br />\n募資連結：<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/reversedfront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeczec.com%2Fprojects%2Freversedfront&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6S3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=6a986b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zeczec.com/projects/reversedfront</a><br />\n<br />\n距離1000萬新台幣目前仲有一段距離<br />\n請各位幫手推post,募資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949551fb8cbdee9ff03edf308ddc4997fa5bc406","tid":2169272,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"已課<br />\n<br />\n諗緊買唔買埋設定集"},{"pid":"83430b0f5044e828e676d6c3fd4f298baad13088","tid":2169272,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"想玩玩了"},{"pid":"6b4a4840a23266a8306da8de99fc3bb18e842cee","tid":2169272,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T19:06:03.000Z","msg":"係咪有準備開發電子版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}